oc:kn_0a871027 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When creating ad creative assets" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Primary text is limited to 125 characters, headlines to 40 characters, descriptions to 30 characters. Ad images should be 1080x1080 (1:1 ratio). Video durations should be 15-60 seconds." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Meta truncates or rejects creative that exceeds these limits; non-compliant assets waste review time" ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_1ad814d2 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Standard ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When running multiple ad sets within a campaign" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use Campaign Budget Optimization (CBO) to let Meta distribute budget across ad sets automatically based on best-performing audiences." ;
    oc:hasRationale "CBO leverages Meta's algorithm for optimal distribution, typically outperforming manual ad set budget allocation" ;
    oc:severityLevel "LOW" .

oc:kn_40b301a3 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When configuring budget allocation across ad sets" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Allocate approximately 70% of budget to prospecting (finding new audiences) and 30% to retargeting (re-engaging existing audiences)." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Prospecting fills the top of funnel; retargeting converts warm leads. Imbalanced spend either starves growth or wastes on exhausted audiences" ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_713cc2f0 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:PreFlightCheck ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Always before campaign activation" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Before launching any campaign, verify pixel is firing correctly on all key events (PageView, ViewContent, AddToCart, Purchase) and Conversions API deduplication is enabled." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Broken pixel tracking means Meta cannot optimize delivery or attribute conversions, making the campaign effectively blind" ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_78a038e4 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When setting up audience targeting for new campaigns" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Start with broad audiences then refine based on performance data. Use Dynamic Creative to test multiple asset combinations automatically." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Broad audiences give Meta's algorithm more signals to optimize; premature narrowing limits learning phase effectiveness" ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_7af832e9 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When structuring any Facebook/Meta ad campaign" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Follow the 3-level hierarchy: Campaign (objective) → Ad Set (audience + budget) → Ad (creative). Always create campaigns paused, then activate after validation." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Meta Ads enforces a strict hierarchy; misplacing settings at the wrong level causes campaigns to underperform or fail to launch" ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_a52754ad a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:WorkflowStrategy ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When configuring campaign automation rules" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Set up automated rules to: (1) pause ads with CPA > $50 and spend > $100, (2) scale ads with ROAS > 3x by 20% budget increase, (3) alert when frequency > 3." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Automated rules prevent budget waste on underperformers and capitalize on winners without constant manual monitoring" ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_e91abd57 a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When monitoring campaign performance over time" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Never ignore frequency metrics. When frequency exceeds 3, ad fatigue sets in and CPAs rise while ROAS drops." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Showing the same creative too many times to the same audience diminishes returns and can damage brand perception" ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

